<doc id="337850" wikidata="Q1207443" url="?curid=337850" title="King Yuan of Zhou">
<text>King Yuan of Zhou (), personal name Ji Ren, was a king of the Chinese Zhou dynasty. He ruled from 476 BC to 469 BC. He was succeeded by his son, King Zhending.

==Ancestry==
==See also==
