<doc id="337889" wikidata="Q1184838" url="?curid=337889" title="King Si of Zhou">
<text>King Si of Zhou (), personal name Ji Shuxi, was a king of the Chinese Zhou dynasty.

He gained the throne in 441 BC by killing his older brother King Ai, but he was in turn killed by his younger brother King Kao after only five months of rule.

==Ancestry==
